<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ChatLock - Advanced AI Features</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 text-gray-900">

<!-- Main Container -->
<div class="container mx-auto p-8">

    <!-- Title Section -->
    <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-blue-600">🔮 Advanced AI Features</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-700">ChatLock ke powerful AI-driven tools ko discover karo jo aapki social experience ko enhance karte hain. Yeh features aapko personalized aur intuitive experience dene ke liye design kiye gaye hain.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Memory Wall Section -->
    <div class="mb-8 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-500">🧠 Memory Wall</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">ChatLock ka AI aapko aise emotional throwbacks dikhata hai jo aapke current mood se relevant hote hain. Yani ki, aapko random “one year ago” wale reminders nahi milte, balki aapke liye meaningful ya motivating posts jo aapke mood se match karti hain.</p>
        <ul class="list-inside list-disc text-gray-700 mt-4">
            <li><strong>Happy memories</strong> jab aapko tough week chal raha ho.</li>
            <li><strong>Motivational posts</strong> jo purani posts se milti hain.</li>
            <li><strong>Past ko thoughtfully resurface</strong> karna jo aapko emotionally connect kare.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- AI Story Remix Section -->
    <div class="mb-8 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-500">🧵 AI Story Remix</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">Aap jo bhi story upload karenge, ChatLock ka AI instantly captions, background music, aur filters/suggestions dega jo aapki story ke emotional vibe se match karein. Yeh bilkul ek smart creative director ki tarah kaam karega.</p>
        <ul class="list-inside list-disc text-gray-700 mt-4">
            <li><strong>Dynamic captions</strong> jo aapki story ke tone ko enhance karein.</li>
            <li><strong>Background music</strong> jo aapki story ke mood ko perfectly match karein.</li>
            <li><strong>Filter/font styles</strong> jo aapke post ke emotion ke according ho.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Post Rewriting Assistant Section -->
    <div class="mb-8 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-500">🧙 Post Rewriting Assistant</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">Kya aapko apne post ka wording thik karne mein dikkat ho rahi hai? ChatLock ka AI aapko calm, funny, bold, ya motivational tones mein posts rewrite karne mein madad karega, taaki aap apne message ko accurately convey kar sakein.</p>
        <ul class="list-inside list-disc text-gray-700 mt-4">
            <li><strong>Calm</strong> tone jo peaceful aur balanced ho.</li>
            <li><strong>Funny</strong> tone jo light-hearted aur entertaining ho.</li>
            <li><strong>Bold</strong> tone jo strong aur assertive ho.</li>
            <li><strong>Motivational</strong> tone jo uplifting aur inspiring ho.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- ShadowBlock AI Section -->
    <div class="mb-8 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-500">🕵️ ShadowBlock AI</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">ChatLock ka ShadowBlock AI fake, toxic, ya ghost followers ko identify karta hai unke behavior ke basis pe. Aap in followers ko silently restrict ya block kar sakte ho bina koi drama create kiye. Aur yeh shady unlock requests ko bhi auto-decline karta hai sensitive posts ke liye.</p>
        <ul class="list-inside list-disc text-gray-700 mt-4">
            <li><strong>Toxic ya fake followers ko detect karein</strong> unke engagement patterns se.</li>
            <li><strong>Quietly block ya restrict karein</strong> problematic followers ko.</li>
            <li><strong>Auto-decline karein shady unlock requests</strong> ke liye Vault posts.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Predictive Privacy Settings Section -->
    <div class="mb-8 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-500">🔒 Predictive Privacy Settings</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">Post publish karne se pehle, ChatLock ka AI aapke content ke tone, sensitivity, aur aapke network ke active members ko dekh ke privacy ke best settings suggest karta hai. Yeh automatically aapki privacy ensure karta hai.</p>
        <ul class="list-inside list-disc text-gray-700 mt-4">
            <li><strong>Privacy settings suggest karein</strong> based on content's tone aur sensitivity.</li>
            <li><strong>AI ke through optimal LockMode settings</strong> suggest karein post publish karne se pehle.</li>
            <li><strong>Automatically ensure karein</strong> privacy sensitive posts ke liye.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- AutoPersona Switch Assistant Section -->
    <div class="mb-8 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-500">👤 AutoPersona Switch Assistant</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">Agar aap apni personal account pe work-related art post kar rahe ho, toh koi tension nahi. ChatLock ka AI aapke post ke context ke hisaab se persona switch karne ke liye suggest karega ya automatically switch karega, taaki aapka profile clean rahe.</p>
        <ul class="list-inside list-disc text-gray-700 mt-4">
            <li><strong>AI automatically switch karega</strong> persona based on post context.</li>
            <li><strong>Profile hygiene maintain karega</strong> across different personas.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Context-Aware VaultChat Replies Section -->
    <div class="mb-8 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-500">📩 Context-Aware VaultChat Replies</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">VaultChat ka smart reply system AI ki madad se suggest karta hai aise replies jo message ke emotional tone ke according ho. Yeh ensure karta hai ki aapke conversations sensitive, positive, ya assertive ho, jo bhi situation ki zarurat ho.</p>
        <ul class="list-inside list-disc text-gray-700 mt-4">
            <li><strong>Emotionally appropriate replies</strong> jo conversation ke tone ko match karein.</li>
            <li><strong>Smart conversation management</strong> jo misunderstandings se bachaye.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- AI-Forged Friend Circles Section -->
    <div class="mb-8 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-500">🧠 AI-Forged Friend Circles</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">AI aapke followers ko dynamic social circles mein divide karta hai based on interaction patterns, jaise “True Vibes”, “Mutual Creators”, aur “Ghost Followers”. Yeh aapko smarter posting decisions lene mein madad karta hai.</p>
        <ul class="list-inside list-disc text-gray-700 mt-4">
            <li><strong>True Vibes</strong> — log jo aapki posts ko frequently engage karte hain.</li>
            <li><strong>Mutual Creators</strong> — creators jo aapke content ko interact karte hain.</li>
            <li><strong>Ghost Followers</strong> — log jo aapke posts par interaction nahi karte.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
